Some common problems and feedback:

1. When importing files, it shows that the files are not legal?

   If you are prompted that the file is not legal, you need to check if your file is corrupted and try again. You can also convert the file format to a common format and then import it.

2. When I try to listen to it, it will not work after processing the circle?

   This is most likely a file compatibility issue, so we suggest you convert the file to another format and try again. If that doesn't work, you can send the file to yueyin.music@foxmail.com and we will do our best to check the cause and release a fix as soon as possible.

